{"tid":172493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民得三百票，投晒俾胡國興又有乜作用？其實連登仔覺得點先係正確？","createTime":"2017-03-26T02:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T03:22:40.000Z","uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a38b6a1d6617ddca47e34887af22cf4ddd69f1a","tid":172493,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"三百票俾胡國興=放棄三百票<br />\n剩低九百票俾建制考慮林鄭or薯片<br />\n泛民完全放棄發揮影響力<br />\n係咪咁樣先符合連登仔個主流價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班人話薯片撐831、推23<br />\n咁林鄭當選就唔會？<br />\n<br />\n如果結局只能二選一<br />\n點解泛民唔應該稍為發揮影響力，趕走一個有可能走極端獨裁路線既人？<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話薯片都有機會變臉，但未來係點邊個會知？講黎都多餘<br />\n<br />\n仲有d人話期望焦土，想林鄭激發佔中2.0，3.0，4.0&hellip;<br />\n但有無諗過『佔中失敗』+『被捕者下場』可能已經令大部份人失去抗爭動力/興趣？<br />\n分分鐘林鄭激發唔到佔中之餘，只係令更多人選擇移民or接受現實(學左班廢老咁)<br />\n焦土個結果係點無人知，但過程會好痛苦就係人都知，點解要支持、期望焦土？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，我無講過薯片係好人，亦唔覺得應該要盲目支持佢or過份期待佢會有咩優秀表現，只係覺得泛民投薯片基本上係無做錯，唔知道連登仔仲有咩高見覺得泛民可以做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0463b52f5f11bc5fcd470af6aa6a59a73db24a","tid":172493,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩你都冇得投票"},{"pid":"532f7443349f02f87d826e87a738c68b0c814913","tid":172493,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc16061034dd4d2cc7f408901b94b1c0d1ab4c4","tid":172493,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩你都冇得投票</blockquote><br />\nAgee<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3708eea59ee7ec4ff55f38f192c48f868a8e0c","tid":172493,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩你都冇得投票</blockquote><br />\n就係唔關事都咁多人屌泛民，但又唔知佢地有咩高見，所以先想問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785697777bf1b233e2a2dd0d069b572d462ffa7b","tid":172493,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"點解總會有班人咁鍾意含撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6c6026c8ac5b80b18d23d3699f7845d7a1ff7e","tid":172493,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"泛民做咩decision佢地都屌架啦<br />\n人地多次講到明票源相近唔搞你泛民搞邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63dbe406052c22a2d6f4a92f1c6d8d50c1fe79b","tid":172493,"uid":76293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"依家連登仔話要民主呀，咪杯個選舉囉，<br />\n都唔諗下邊到比到個民主你，唔好ff咁多啦，學識接受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c66ab7adc71803f229de3abeb8e5ba9def374","tid":172493,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"580da1be7875ee3cb327def3bbea617430ace1c8","tid":172493,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登激進派全力支持射鳩晒落海 總之投薯片就仆街含家產 投胡官就憨鳩 投奶媽就係命中註定係天意 同佢地講道理係晒氣 跟隊射晒落海佢地最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：3個都唔撐"},{"pid":"e11df7815223117156eb557d9381a49abb450a55","tid":172493,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解總會有班人咁鍾意含撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>